{"tid":1995583,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"英男口角後掟妻落樓致重傷　站原地合十祈禱兩小時","createTime":"2020-04-30T11:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T12:12:23.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"488f5f67c3a4567b89d5a03da64d2876d748bed5","tid":1995583,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200430/_2020043016450052965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200430%2F_2020043016450052965.jpg&h=fb5f4fdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後戴夫一直站在陽台上，雙手合十狀似祈禱。 網圖<br />\n<br />\n泰國羅勇府周二發生一件離奇案件，46歲的英籍男子戴夫與泰籍妻子發生口角後，疑將老婆從8樓掟下去，他事後站在原地，雙手合十禱告多個小時，最後才向警方坦言，因為悶在家中太久，壓力過大，才會發生口角。<br />\n<br />\n據當地媒體報導，56歲的泰籍女子蘇坎達從8樓陽台墜下，倒臥在7樓身受重傷，意識清醒大叫求救，當地警方與救援小組趕到現場，將傷者送院搶救，女子證實髖部骨折，左手臂脫臼。她向警方表示，自己是被丈夫推下樓。<br />\n<br />\n事後戴夫一直站在陽台上，雙手合十狀似祈禱，對旁人的說話沒有任何反應。有關單位最終只好聯繫當事人的朋友前來協助，但朋友大叫多時依然得不到回應。戴夫「神遊」超過2小時後，終於打開門讓大樓管理員與移民局官員進入。他透露，因為幾個月絕少外出，導致壓力很大、氣氛緊張，才會發生爭吵，釀成妻子墜樓的意外。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，戴夫是合法入境，目前因疫情關係無法返回英國。警方正等待蘇坎達傷勢復原後再作調查，釐清這場意外發生的真正原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1759621/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%92%E5%BE%8C%E6%8E%9F%E5%A6%BB%E8%90%BD%E6%A8%93%E8%87%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7-%E7%AB%99%E5%8E%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%88%E5%8D%81%E7%A5%88%E7%A6%B1%E5%85%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1759621%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%258E%259F%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25A5%2588%25E7%25A6%25B1%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZ8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=32e5bef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1759621%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%258E%259F%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A8%2593%25E8%2587%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25A5%2588%25E7%25A6%25B1%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582&h=ae111c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1759621/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%A3%E8%A7%92%E5%BE%8C%E6%8E%9F%E5%A6%BB%E8%90%BD%E6%A8%93%E8%87%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7-%E7%AB%99%E5%8E%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%88%E5%8D%81%E7%A5%88%E7%A6%B1%E5%85%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82</a>"},{"pid":"dce6579ddf9cbdafc12024620a4d4dde18f90c07","tid":1995583,"uid":76753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:03:54.000Z","msg":"點解小明由8樓跳落樓都唔死"},{"pid":"596a354bcf46000184d83a683e1a3c4f1d9f4e49","tid":1995583,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"唉又被人掟落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e176127755fcd506840241f038a3e6a0fe2c4b5","tid":1995583,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:04:58.000Z","msg":"係咪輸油輸到傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9947ffbc7aa2d7a7fe3e842d8a44e3ad498b603a","tid":1995583,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"戴夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dc3dace3875384d79f26f5c673a502f4ede1ee","tid":1995583,"uid"